{"tid":139301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登仔同中國人一樣 係一班被圈養嘅豬","createTime":"2017-03-01T10:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T10:42:15.000Z","uid":4493,"like":66,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e5762bbebf0cb66590e239db5ab2744d4e9b95","tid":139301,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"iProA, 613大屠殺, 篤灰...<br />\n(要重溫可以按下面)<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/林祖舜\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E6%9E%97%E7%A5%96%E8%88%9C&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8702cac8\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/林祖舜</a><br />\n<br />\n今次有連登巴打自己柒被早洩KO之後，高登終於威番一次，成班高登豬竟然清一色支持林祖舜，踩鳩反騙徒嘅巴打！<br />\n<br />\n臉書中出現大量「牙joe好嘢！多謝牙joe!」的留言。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母！根本同支那人冇分別！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根本就同一班食完有毒食物，間屋比城管拆咗，條女比富二代強姦，比國企拖糧； 但仲會出街大叫我愛中國，打倒日本鬼子嘅支那畜冇分別！<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，比較有獨立思考能力嘅高登仔已經全部過檔連登，亦可見林祖舜已經成功用斯德哥爾摩症候群控制高登論壇。<br />\n<br />\n林祖舜我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"18b08a25bb3285d64ae8872132c4a8486751ecd0","tid":139301,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"0894e89d3ad23d97c2042683fed93b1e13f348e3","tid":139301,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"咁想要正評比你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on撚鳩"},{"pid":"9dc5da7278d16a2f965abaf8d00d42245ceba667","tid":139301,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正</blockquote><br />\n亦要注意連高兩登兩邊走嘅會員，佢哋嘅價值觀同埋分析能力好有可能已經受到嚴重影響，退化至中國人水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef7174298f1aed10cddc9ce6519c66b25d5d713","tid":139301,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"膠登開果陣已經知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n雖然膠登都唔係好好"},{"pid":"64d08f11f4b7d996d55eccfe953f0792b97d872a","tid":139301,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>膠登開果陣已經知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n雖然膠登都唔係好好</blockquote><br />\n但至少以前會人人屌admin老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家變埋支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39916cc35144d4c4ae6d3bc657b68568a70c14e5","tid":139301,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"上連登的高登打手 = 翻牆五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34812083d997ddbd8030ea1a9ef00bf054a7471","tid":139301,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"同 windows 藍畫面，中毒，偷資料，仲要繼續用 windows 一樣"},{"pid":"fd7bfd2b4a20ef56d383f03b31ee55b548772b37","tid":139301,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同 windows 藍畫面，中毒，偷資料，仲要繼續用 windows 一樣</blockquote><br />\n咁都抽到水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f113b3cbad4d4873dae083ec3382fc628e3b065","tid":139301,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同 windows 藍畫面，中毒，偷資料，仲要繼續用 windows 一樣</blockquote><br />\n我冇事喎"},{"pid":"9ff6923c5379b8186da950eef01696814662a0ec","tid":139301,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"bam淨嘅高登仔思想係點，大家心目有數"},{"pid":"31dabfea2c0894c58028012881d573c290bb8d8c","tid":139301,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>膠登開果陣已經知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n雖然膠登都唔係好好</bl